# Desktop Hazel Rules - February 2026 SOTA Best Practices
# Ultra-aggressive auto-organization for clean workspace
# Based on 2026 trends: Zero Desktop, Lifecycle-based archiving, AI-ready metadata

## Rule 1: Screenshots - Instant Processing
Name: Auto-import Screenshots to Photos
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Name contains "Screen" OR "Screenshot" OR "screen"
  - Kind is Image
Do the following:
  - Import into Photos.app
  - Move to Trash
  - Play sound "Submarine"

## Rule 2: Code Files - Route to Appropriate Repo
Name: Code files to Workspace
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Extension is js, ts, tsx, jsx, py, go, rs, java, kt, swift
  - Age is greater than 1 day
Do the following:
  - Add tags: "code", "needs-review"
  - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/1-Active/Projects/Code-Snippets/
  - Display notification "Code file moved to Active Projects"

## Rule 3: Large Files - Immediate Archive
Name: Large files (>500MB) to Google Drive
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Size is greater than 500 MB
  - Date Last Modified is less than 7 days ago
Do the following:
  - Add tags: "large-file", "auto-archived"
  - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/Large-Archives/
  - Display notification "Large file archived: [filename]"

## Rule 4: Documents - Smart Categorization
Name: PDF documents by type
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Extension is pdf
  - Age is greater than 2 days
Do the following:
  - If Name contains "invoice" OR "receipt":
    - Add tags: "finance", "receipt"
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Receipts/
  - Else if Name contains "visa" OR "immigration" OR "green card" OR "uscis":
    - Add tags: "immigration", "important"
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Immigration/
  - Else:
    - Add tags: "document"
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Documents/

## Rule 5: Images - Smart Storage
Name: Images to organized folders
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Kind is Image
  - Extension is not (jpg, jpeg, png) matching screenshots
  - Age is greater than 7 days
Do the following:
  - If Date Last Modified is less than 30 days ago:
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/1-Active/Personal/Recent-Images/
  - Else:
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Images/

## Rule 6: Videos - Archive by size and age
Name: Videos lifecycle management
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Kind is Movie
  - Age is greater than 3 days
Do the following:
  - If Size is greater than 1 GB:
    - Move to: ~/Movies/Large-Videos/
  - Else:
    - Move to: ~/Movies/

## Rule 7: Old Files - Aggressive 30-day cleanup
Name: Files older than 30 days to Archive
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Date Last Modified is more than 30 days ago
  - Name does not contain "00-Active" OR "01-In-Progress"
  - Kind is not Folder
Do the following:
  - Add tags: "auto-archived", "30-day-cleanup"
  - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Desktop-Archive/[YYYY-MM]/

## Rule 8: Installers - Auto-cleanup
Name: DMG and ZIP installers cleanup
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Extension is dmg OR zip OR pkg
  - Age is greater than 7 days
Do the following:
  - Move to Trash
  - Display notification "Cleaned up installer: [filename]"

## Rule 9: Folders - Project lifecycle
Name: Project folders auto-archive
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Kind is Folder
  - Name does not contain "00-Active" OR "01-In-Progress" OR "ProjectQueue"
  - Date Last Opened is more than 14 days ago
Do the following:
  - Add tags: "project", "inactive"
  - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/2-Workspace/Inactive-Projects/
  - Display notification "Inactive project archived: [foldername]"

## Rule 10: Empty folders - Immediate removal
Name: Remove empty folders
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Kind is Folder
  - Contents is empty
  - Age is greater than 1 day
Do the following:
  - Move to Trash

## Rule 11: Duplicate files - Smart deduplication
Name: Remove obvious duplicates
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Name contains " (1)" OR " (2)" OR " copy" OR "_0"
  - Age is greater than 3 days
Do the following:
  - Add tags: "duplicate", "needs-review"
  - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/Duplicates-Review-Jan-2026/

## Rule 12: Text files - Context-aware routing
Name: Text and markdown files
If ALL of the following conditions are met:
  - Extension is txt OR md OR markdown
  - Age is greater than 2 days
Do the following:
  - If Name contains "todo" OR "task":
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/3-TODO/
  - Else if Name contains "note" OR "idea":
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Journal/
  - Else:
    - Move to: ~/Library/CloudStorage/GoogleDrive-hank.lee.qed@gmail.com/My Drive/My Drive/Archive/2025/Personal/Documents/

# 2026 Best Practices Applied:
# - Zero Desktop Philosophy: Nothing stays longer than needed
# - Lifecycle-based: Different retention for different file types
# - Context-aware: Uses filename patterns for smart routing
# - AI-ready: Consistent tagging for future AI organization
# - Cloud-first: Everything goes to Google Drive for backup
# - Aggressive: 7-30 day cleanup cycles
